      This tells the application to map the location
      <mapthisdrive>true</mapthisdrive>
      
      The name of the shared directory to map
      <sharename>\\192.168.1.100\sharefile</sharename>
      
      The local drive letter to map the share to.
      If the directory is on the local machine, put the path here
      <localdrive>N:</localdrive>
      
      The username for the shared directory
      <username>fakeuser</username>
      
      The password for the shared directory
      <password>badpassword</password>
    -->

    <!-- Example values for local locations
      Set to false for local paths
      <mapthisdrive>false</mapthisdrive>
      
      Leave empty for local paths
      <sharename></sharename>
      
      The local path
      <localdrive>N:</localdrive>
      
      Leave empty for local path
      <username>fakeuser</username>
      
